      "content": "i dont think i can do this anymore. everything i worked for is just... gone. the lab results, the funding, all the years of being 'the smart one'. it feels like i'm just a ghost walking around a campus that doesn't even want me here. i'm so tired of trying to fix things that are fundamentally broken. i just want the noise to stop.",
